==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ophidian
<hw>O*phid"i*an</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>ophidien</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to
